data.description: HUD Owned Home, case number 241-857962. HUD Homes are sold "as is," FHA insurable with repair escrow, subject to appraisal. Exciting opportunity to own this solid brick end of  the group townhome in the neighborhood of  Ritchie Heights! Upon entering the home, you will be welcomed with a large living room, a full bath and a nice sized kitchen with wood cabinets and appliances. The upper level features two spacious bedrooms and a full bath with soaking tub. Enjoy the outdoor activities in the fenced backyard or relax on the front porch with nice view of the street. Home is located near schools, parks and eighteen minutes travel to  BWI Airport.
